---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const bathroomShowcaseItems = await Astro.glob(
	"../../public/showcase/bathrooms/*.jpeg",
);
---

<Layout title="Homeowners">
	<div
		class="min-h-screen px-8 flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 py-16"
	>
		<section class="flex flex-col space-y-8 items-center mt-8">
			<h1 class="heading">Bathroom Remodel</h1>
			<p class="leading-relaxed max-w-5xl">
				If you're a homeowner looking to update your
				home, consider a bathroom remodel. It's more
				than just a fresh lookâ€”it's a smart investment.
				Contrary to the belief that such renovations are
				expensive, they actually offer a substantial
				return according to real estate experts. Looking
				to enhance your home's value and comfort?
				Explore our list of bathroom remodeling ideas.
				Interested? Contact us for a free estimate and
				turn your bathroom into a profitable investment.
			</p>

			<img
				src="/showcase/bathrooms/1.jpeg"
				alt=""
				class="h-96 aspect-video"
			/>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
				{
					bathroomShowcaseItems.map((item, i) => {
						return (
							<img
								src={
									item
										.default
										.src
								}
								alt=""
								class="w-36 mx-auto aspect-[9/14] object-cover"
							/>
						);
					})
				}
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="flex flex-col space-y-8 items-center mt-8">
			<h1 class="heading">Kitchen Remodel</h1>
			<p class="leading-relaxed max-w-5xl">
				With decades of expertise in residential
				projects, Caspers Construction has masterfully
				transformed countless kitchens, consistently
				exceeding our clients' expectations. Our team of
				seasoned professionals excels in efficient
				installations, ensuring a swift project
				turnaround without compromising quality. At
				Caspers Construction, we are passionately
				committed to turning your dream kitchen into a
				reality.
			</p>

			<img
				src="/showcase/Kitchen/1.jpeg"
				alt=""
				class="h-96 aspect-video"
			/>
		</section>

		<section
			id="complete-home"
			class="flex flex-col space-y-8 items-center mt-8"
		>
			<h1 class="heading">Complete Home Remodel</h1>
			<p class="leading-relaxed max-w-5xl">
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
				adipisicing elit. Ipsum veritatis corporis nihil
				consectetur suscipit! Enim recusandae itaque,
				quo vitae iure ut illo consequuntur illum
				deserunt accusamus minima dignissimos, quae
				veniam distinctio odit in. Adipisci non
				repellendus molestiae, repellat tempore nihil ex
				assumenda quos dolore neque sed sapiente
				exercitationem nostrum ipsam quasi aliquam!
				Culpa, incidunt. Omnis eaque autem maxime
				excepturi impedit esse facere rerum aperiam
				expedita, odit soluta. Corrupti doloremque
